---
title: "Analysis of the UK Biobank data"
---

We apply KnockoffZoom to some traits in the [UK Biobank](https://www.ukbiobank.ac.uk/) data and obtain many new findings. To learn more, read the accompanying paper.

To explore our results interactively, visit: [https://msesia.shinyapps.io/knockoffzoom/](https://msesia.shinyapps.io/knockoffzoom/)
